<section class="landing">
  <div class="landing-inner">
    <h1>Canadian grain grading data, <em>machine-readable</em> at last.</h1>
    <p class="description">
      The Canadian Grain Commission publishes official grade determinant tables
      as PDFs and HTML pages. Grading Factors converts that data into a clean,
      structured API - free to use, openly documented, and updated each crop year.
    </p>
    <a href="/getting-started/overview" class="cta-button">Get API Key</a>
    <a href="/getting-started/overview" class="docs-link">Already have a key? Browse the docs →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .landing {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #0d1320;
  }

  .landing-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 790px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    word-break: keep-all;
    overflow-wrap: normal;
}

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
}

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #00e5b0;
    color: #0d1320;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .docs-link {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    text-decoration: none;
   }

  .docs-link:hover {
    color: #00e5b0;
   }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
   .landing {
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }
   .landing-inner {
        text-align: left;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    .description {
        font-size: 1rem;
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    .cta-button {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }
}
</style>